00:17:26.080 --> 00:17:30.560
[Amit Varma]: one vote is not going to do much so it is rational for them to be ignorant that's called

00:17:30.560 --> 00:17:35.680
[Amit Varma]: rational ignorance and in fact there's a philosopher jason brennan who will be on my

